#PF sense

PF sense is a fully customizable distro that can change any computer into a fireawall and router. The computer must have two access cards and if you have compact flash storage you should use embedded version of PF sense. Pf sense has other popular uses as listed below.

LAN/WAN Router
Internet Cafes
Wireless Hotspot (Captive Portal)
VPN Router
Firewall
DHCP / DNS Server
Wireless Access Point
Transparent Squid Proxy Server
Multi Wan Router or Load Balancer
DNS Blacklist
Port Forwarding / NAT (Network Address Translation)